 |my = 避孕套<ref>{{Cite web|title=少女上网谴责情侣胡搞 戏院座位留下已用过避孕套 {{!}} 国际|url=https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/international/2021/12/22/457519|access-date=2022-03-29|date=2021-12-22|work=東方網 馬來西亞東方日報|language=zh-Hans|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405184849/https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/news/international/2021/12/22/457519}}</ref>、如意套
